At 1500 hours on March 5, the epidemic prevention and Control Headquarters of Xi'an high-tech zone confirmed to the _ paper _ (www.thepaper.cn ) that, the epidemic prevention and control headquarters in Zhangba Street, Xi'an High-tech Zone, issued a notice on March 5 on strict isolation and observation measures for Unit 2, building 1, Rome, the notice said the district identified a confirmed case of COVID-19, and the patient's building unit under strict surveillance measures.

The Xi'an High-tech Zone Epidemic Prevention and Control Command said it would release more details later.

As mentioned in the above-mentioned notice on strict quarantine measures for the second unit of the first building in Rome, a confirmed case of COVID-19 has been identified in the second unit of the first building in Sicily, Rome. The patient has been admitted to a designated hospital and his family members have been placed under medical isolation. In order to ensure the safety of all residents in the community and reduce the risk of infection, in accordance with the relevant provisions of the Law of the People's Republic of China on the Prevention and control of infectious diseases and the notice of the Headquarters Office of the prevention and control of pneumonia in Xi'an COVID-19 on the strict isolation of observation objects and areas at home (No. 24[2020] issued by the Municipal Committee Office) , and the high-tech zone epidemic prevention and control headquarters on March 5,04:01, the command is now one building in Rome Sicily, two units to take strict isolation measures (lifting time notice) .

The notice said that during the closure period, the requirements for household necessities such as grain, oil, vegetables and so on will be fully protected, and professional disinfection units will be organized to carry out disinfection and sterilization of this building. Please keep calm and mind, stay at home and watch, do not go out, wash hands frequently, more ventilation, common resistance to epidemic disease, household garbage please according to the provisions of time outside the door, the Organization of a unified collection and transportation.
